{"tid":1509902,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"仲忍個柒婆，開佢拖啦，揸爆機場呢個春袋","createTime":"2019-08-27T03:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T23:42:21.000Z","uid":143569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b21b37c65f36de8e03acb871d7254a6cb54263b5","tid":1509902,"uid":143569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"香港特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前會見記者。昨日有傳媒報道，她曾在青年廣場與市民對話，提到政府不設獨立調查委員會是因警隊抗拒。她今日否認此事，指不設獨立調查委員會是因監警會已能調查。她又批評威者在過去的周六日，「暴力升級」，警方是用「最低武力」保護自己。她重申，政府不是不回應示威者訴求，而是不接受這些訴求 ...<br />\n<br />\n不接受呀，屌佢老母，踩到上心口"},{"pid":"01917c793eb0a55c3c1cd11d6cd970807d105450","tid":1509902,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=8a9d6531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=e39d309d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=149ddd58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"f2a865d3819f749763f6087c5a44fa144bc750aa","tid":1509902,"uid":125553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxEUeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2